sequenceDiagram
    participant User as Data Scientist
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Webhook as Webhook Server<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Controller as Predictor Controller<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    participant ModelMesh as ModelMesh gRPC<br/>8085/TCP plaintext
    participant etcd as etcd<br/>2379/TCP HTTP plaintext
    participant Adapter as Runtime Adapter
    participant S3 as S3/MinIO<br/>443/9000 HTTPS/HTTP
    participant Server as Model Server<br/>8001/TCP gRPC plaintext
    participant Client as Inference Client

    Note over User,S3: Flow 1: Model Deployment via InferenceService

    User->>K8sAPI: Create InferenceService<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: Validate CR<br/>TLS 1.2+ K8s API Token
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Validation Result
    K8sAPI-->>User: CR Created

    Controller->>K8sAPI: Watch InferenceService<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI->>Controller: CR Event

    Controller->>ModelMesh: Register Model<br/>8085/TCP gRPC plaintext
    ModelMesh->>etcd: Store Model Metadata<br/>2379/TCP HTTP plaintext

    ModelMesh->>Adapter: Load Model Request
    Adapter->>S3: Download Model Artifacts<br/>AWS IAM or Access Keys
    S3-->>Adapter: Model Files
    Adapter->>Server: Load Model into Runtime
    Server-->>Adapter: Model Loaded
    Adapter-->>ModelMesh: Model Ready
    ModelMesh-->>Controller: Deployment Complete

    Note over Client,Server: Flow 2: Model Inference Request

    Client->>ModelMesh: Inference Request<br/>8033/TCP gRPC plaintext/mTLS
    ModelMesh->>etcd: Get Model Location<br/>2379/TCP HTTP
    etcd-->>ModelMesh: Model Pod Info
    ModelMesh->>Server: Forward Request<br/>8001/TCP gRPC plaintext
    Server-->>ModelMesh: Inference Result
    ModelMesh-->>Client: Response

    Note over User,Webhook: Flow 3: ServingRuntime Validation

    User->>K8sAPI: Create ServingRuntime<br/>Bearer Token
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: Validate ServingRuntime<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    Webhook->>K8sAPI: Get Runtime Config<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>Webhook: Validation Data
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Validation Result
    K8sAPI-->>User: ServingRuntime Created
